 Nichts als Elend! - ab.  afunded by Swiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 4aBern. 4aEuropäische Geschichte. 4aGeldstag. 4aGeschichte des 19. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichte. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aGesellschaft. 4aKonkurs. 4aKredit. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aScheitern. 4aSchulden. 4aSchweiz. 4aSozialgeschichte. 4aWirtschaft. 4aWirtschaftsgeschichte. 4aÖkonomie. 7aHISTORY / Europe / General.2bisacsh  aBankruptcy.  aBern.  aCredit.  aCultural History.  aDebts.  aEconomic History.  aEconomy.  aEuropean History.  aFailure.  aHistory of the 19th Century.  aHistory.  aMoneyday.  aSocial History.  aSociety.  aSwitzerland.2 aSwiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2023z9783111024950oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839466421?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839466421zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839466421/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-TGPb2023